
<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/sawarabimincho.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cinzel+Decorative:400,700,900" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">

    <meta name="description" content= {{description}}>
    <meta name="theme-color" content="RoyalBlue">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/icon/favicon.png">
    <title>{{title}} - Fully Hatter の秘密の部屋</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-head">
                <nav class="navbar is-pulled-right" role="navigation" aria-label="main navigation">
                    <div class="navbar-brand">
                        <a class="navbar-item" href="/">
                            <div class="title is-3"><span class="orange-title">F</span>ully <span class="orange-title">H</span>atter の秘密の部屋</div>
                        </a>
                        <a class="navbar-item" href="https://twitter.com/FullyHatter">
                            <figure class="image is-24x24">
                                <img src="/images/icon/twitter.png" alt="Twitter logo">
                            </figure>
                        </a>
                        <a class="navbar-item" href="https://github.com/FullyHatter">
                            <figure class="image is-24x24">
                                <img src="/images/icon/github.png" alt="GitHub logo">
                            </figure>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </nav>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-body">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1 class="title is-2">{{title}}</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </header>
    {{{pagination}}}
    {{{body}}}
    {{{pagination}}}
    {{{comments}}}
    <footer class="footer">
        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="columns">
                    <div class="column is-three-fifths">
                        <a href="/"><h1 class="title is-3"><span class="orange-title">F</span>ully <span class="orange-title">H</span>atter の秘密の部屋</h1></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column">
                        <iframe
                            src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets/follow_button.html?screen_name=FullyHatter"
                            title="Follow FullyHatter on Twitter"
                            width="250"
                            height="40"
                            style="border: 0; overflow: hidden;">
                        </iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>
                    テキストは引用部分以外すべて著作権を放棄しています。コピペ、盗用などご自由にどうぞ！
